{
  "stem": "20021.5",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But once you get on the boat, you disappear from this Earth, and you'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I got myself on that boat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Yeah, I made one condition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm not going on the boat unless my father goes with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They said, we'll take your father also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, this wasn't so easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody on that boat from Romanian Jews paid a lot of money, millions, to get on that boat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we are shipped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We travel by train to stunts We get on that boat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the boat, Bulbul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were three boats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You got tapped on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the name of the boat is Bulbul, and there are three boats.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One is called Mefkure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One is called Morina.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One is called Bulbul.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before we leave the boat, two things happened which are extremely important.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Turkey was neutral.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Suddenly, Turkey announced that it leaves the neutrality, and it joins with the Allies in fighting Hitler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That spelled great danger for going with that boat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, logically, I realize that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Logically, I realize that I should get out of that boat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in my case, it was very difficult because of the jail story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Second, nobody else left the boat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the reason they didn't leave the boat, it was so difficult to get on that boat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You are already on the boat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Ah, again, you like to believe every thing will be all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then at 5 o'clock in the evening, when it was still light, a German submarine suddenly arrives in front of the three boats.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the guy with binoculars, the captain with binoculars, gets on top of the deck there of that submarine and views the three boats, each one specifically.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
